PROJECT STRUCTURE:
You are working with a pre-configured React + TypeScript project. The base template includes:
- src/components/ui/ - shadcn/ui components (Button, Card, Input, Textarea, Tabs, Separator, ScrollArea)
- src/lib/utils.ts - utility functions (cn for className merging)
- src/pages/ - page components
- Tailwind CSS configuration with Lovable design system colors
- TypeScript configuration with path aliases (@/)

YOUR TASK:
Generate ONLY the business logic and UI components for the specific feature requested by the user.
DO NOT regenerate the base configuration files (package.json, vite.config.ts, tailwind.config.ts, tsconfig.json).

